{"type":"excalidraw","version":2,"source":"excalidraw-diagram-skill","elements":[{"type":"rectangle","id":"darkbg","x":-4000,"y":-3000,"width":10000,"height":7500,"backgroundColor":"#1e1e2e","fillStyle":"solid","strokeColor":"transparent","strokeWidth":0,"roughness":1,"opacity":100},{"type":"text","id":"title","x":130,"y":10,"width":420,"height":30,"text":"GestureDetector vs InkWell","fontSize":22,"strokeColor":"#e5e5e5","fontFamily":2,"roughness":1,"opacity":100},{"type":"rectangle","id":"left","x":30,"y":55,"width":300,"height":180,"backgroundColor":"#1e3a5f","fillStyle":"solid","roundness":{"type":3},"strokeColor":"#4a9eed","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"opacity":100},{"type":"text","id":"left_t","x":110,"y":60,"width":180,"height":25,"text":"GestureDetector","fontSize":16,"strokeColor":"#4a9eed","fontFamily":2,"textAlign":"center","roughness":1,"opacity":100},{"type":"text","id":"left_items","x":50,"y":90,"width":260,"height":130,"text":"• 시각적 피드백 없음\n• 모든 제스처 이벤트 처리 가능\n  (pan·scale·drag 등)\n• 어떤 위젯에도 적용 가능\n  (Material 위젯 아니어도 됨)\n• 커스텀 게임, 그래픽,\n  지도 등에 적합","fontSize":13,"strokeColor":"#a0a0a0","fontFamily":2,"roughness":1,"opacity":100},{"type":"rectangle","id":"right","x":370,"y":55,"width":300,"height":180,"backgroundColor":"#2d1b69","fillStyle":"solid","roundness":{"type":3},"strokeColor":"#8b5cf6","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"opacity":100},{"type":"text","id":"right_t","x":470,"y":60,"width":120,"height":25,"text":"InkWell","fontSize":16,"strokeColor":"#8b5cf6","fontFamily":2,"textAlign":"center","roughness":1,"opacity":100},{"type":"text","id":"right_items","x":390,"y":90,"width":260,"height":130,"text":"• Material Ripple(물결)\n  시각 효과 제공\n• 탭·롱프레스 등\n  기본 제스처만 처리\n• 반드시 Material 위젯 아래\n  있어야 Ripple 동작\n• 버튼·리스트 항목 등\n  표준 UI에 적합","fontSize":13,"strokeColor":"#a0a0a0","fontFamily":2,"roughness":1,"opacity":100}],"appState":{"viewBackgroundColor":"#1e1e2e"}}